Package: r2typ
Title: An R Package for Generating Typst Markup
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Joseph", "Barbier", , "joseph@ysunflower.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Translate R functions into valid Typst markup and provide a large number of built-in tools for working with Typst data types, native Typst compilation and Quarto documents.
